real-time.title: Unuhi Manawa maoli
real-time.subtitle: Unuhi ma waena o 40+ mau ʻōlelo pūlima a ʻōlelo ʻia i ka manawa maoli
real-time.description: Hāʻawi kā mākou polokalamu iā ʻoe e kamaʻilio kūlohelohe a maʻalahi me kekahi, ma nā wahi āpau, i kēlā me kēia manawa, ma kāu ʻōlelo hōʻailona ponoʻī.

multilingual.description: Kākoʻo kā mākou polokalamu i nā ʻōlelo hōʻailona he nui a me nā ʻōlelo ʻōlelo, no laila hiki iā ʻoe ke kamaʻilio me nā poʻe mai nā ʻāina a me nā moʻomeheu like ʻole.

appearance.title: Hiki ke nānā aku
appearance.subtitle: Hāʻawi kā mākou kiʻi kiʻi ʻōlelo hōʻailona avatar i kahi ākea o nā koho hoʻoponopono e kūpono i kāu mau pono kikoʻī.
appearance.description: Inā makemake ʻoe e hana i kahi avatar e like me ʻoe a i ʻole e hana i kahi ʻano kūʻokoʻa, ʻo kā mākou koho hoʻoponopono e ʻae iā ʻoe e hōʻike iā ʻoe iho ma ke ʻano he ʻoiaʻiʻo a ʻoiaʻiʻo iā ʻoe.

open-source.description: Ma ka kaʻana like ʻana i kā mākou kumu kumu, manaʻo mākou e hoʻoulu i ka laulima a me ka ʻike.

offline.title: Hana hoʻopahemo
offline.subtitle: E hōʻailona i ka Unuhi ma nā wahi a pau, ʻoiai hoʻopahemo ma ka mokulele.
offline.description: Inā ʻoe e huakaʻi ana, ma kahi mamao, a i ʻole ka punaewele, hōʻoia kā mākou app e hiki iā ʻoe ke unuhi mau i ka ʻōlelo a i ʻole ka ʻōlelo i kākau ʻia i loko o ka ʻōlelo hōʻailona, ​​e mālama ana i nā mea hana kamaʻilio koʻikoʻi ma kou manamana lima.
